OL,3,CMan jailed for killing 'beloved dad'
OL,4,Cwith punch outside Wetherspoon pub
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for more than 10
OL,7,Fyears after punching and killing
OL,8,Fanother man outside a Wetherspoon pub
OL,9,Fbecause he felt "disrespected".
OL,11,FKyle O'Callaghan, 30, previously
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to the manslaughter of
OL,13,FMarcus Carpenter, 37, who died in
OL,14,Fhospital after he was assaulted
OL,15,Foutside the Picture House in Ebbw Vale.
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
