FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778951200
OL,3,CMan jailed for killing 'beloved dad'
OL,4,Cwith punch outside Wetherspoon pub
OL,6,FOn Friday, Judge Williams sentenced
OL,7,FO'Callaghan, of no fixed abode, to 10
OL,8,Fand a half years in prison with an
OL,9,Fextended licence period of four years.
OL,11,FIn a tribute Mr Carpenter's family
OL,12,Fdescribed him as a "beloved son,
OL,13,Fpartner and dad".
OL,15,FThey added: "Marcus was one of a kind
OL,16,Fwith the kindest of hearts who would
OL,17,Fhelp anyone out he could.
OL,19,F"His passing has left a massive hole
OL,20,Fin the lives of everyone close to him."
OL,26,@tD@TOUuD@PO]wD@MOU{D@AOU|D@gO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778951200
OL,3,CMan jailed for killing 'beloved dad'
OL,4,Cwith punch outside Wetherspoon pub
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Neil Blyth,
OL,7,Fof Gwent Police, said: "I'd like to
OL,8,Fpay tribute to the friends and family
OL,9,Fof Mr Carpenter who showed great
OL,10,Fstrength and dignity throughout this
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"I know today's sentencing of
OL,14,FO'Callaghan will never bring Mr
OL,15,FCarpenter back. However, I hope this
OL,16,Foutcome can provide the victim's
OL,17,Ffamily with some measure of justice
OL,18,Fand allows them to start rebuilding
OL,19,Ftheir lives.
OL,26,@oD@XOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778951200
OL,3,CMan jailed for killing 'beloved dad'
OL,4,Cwith punch outside Wetherspoon pub
OL,6,F"I also want to thank the support of
OL,7,Fthe local community, some of whom
OL,8,Fprovided vital evidence to us, for
OL,9,Ftheir help in bringing O'Callaghan to
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,F"I would like to remind our
OL,13,Fcommunities that acts of violence are
OL,14,Fnot acceptable.
OL,16,F"As a result of O'Callaghan's actions,
OL,17,FMr Carpenter was seriously injured
OL,18,Ffollowing an assault and never
OL,19,Frecovered, leaving the lives of his
OL,20,Ffamily and friends forever changed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778951200
OL,3,CMan jailed for killing 'beloved dad'
OL,4,Cwith punch outside Wetherspoon pub
OL,6,F"The circumstances of Mr Carpenter's
OL,7,Fdeath should act as a warning to
OL,8,Fothers as to how a senseless and
OL,9,Fneedless act of violence can lead to
OL,10,Fdevastating consequences."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
